Body:
[for] it is they who have taken error in exchange for guidance;
			and neither has their bargain brought them gain, nor have they
			found guidance [elsewhere].

But there are among them such as pray, "O our Sustainer! Grant us
			good in this world and good in the life to come, and keep us safe
			from suffering through the fire":

And [remember the time] when We vouchsafed unto Moses the divine
			writ - and [thus] a standard by which to discern the true from
			the false <span class='fn'>38</span> - so that you might be guided aright;

And you turned away after that! And had it not been for God's
			favour upon you and His grace, you would surely have found
			yourselves among the lost;
